    public abstract class ActorChannelMessageEventBase<A extends Actor>
extends ActorChannelEventBase<A>
implements MessageEvent
    Abstract base class for events involving an Actor and Channel and have a message. Use the helper events if you want to listen to events involving either.
    See Also:
    ActorEvent, ChannelEvent, MessageEvent
